name: 👺 TIGER CLAN MASK
description:
A unique opportunity has arisen for a new clan leader...

A 48 hour timer has started...
https://itsalmo.st/time-cpy5

To gain possession of the clan mask, you must:
- place a qualifying bid before the timer is up.

A qualifying bid must be:
- made on the objkt.com website via the "offer" button
- made before the timer reaches zero
- 15xtz or more
- 1+ higher than the previous bid
- made by a holder of a samurai of the same clan (one mask/clan per person only).

Bids will be checked for ownership and the highest qualifying bid when the time is up will be accepted and the winner will receive the clan leader title...
